column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.dered_r, p.ra,p.dec,p.petror9#_r, p.dered_g, p_el_mon as elliptical, p_cw_mon as spiralclock, p_acw_mon as spiralanticlock   FROM Galaxy as p    JOIN ZooNoSpec AS zns ON p.objid = zns.objid    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE zns.p_cw># or zns.p_acw># or zns.p_el>#
